{"tid":1625784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個藍到發黑嘅老豆噚晚踢手足","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:04:37.000Z","uid":245626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cc999fd8b11a1b9356c1b19404f7f41c171b6f2d","tid":1625784,"uid":245626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:19:59.000Z","msg":"喺度同嗰位俾我老豆踢嘅手足講聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n初初都知佢深藍<br />\n平時喺條街度都會話手足係仆街同曱甴，驚死人唔知佢藍咁，成日撩是鬥非<br />\n又時不時wtsapp啲廢老藍絲片俾我<br />\n我一話返佢同send返啲文宣俾佢佢就勁燥<br />\n仲話我癲倒是非，食屎屙飯<br />\n佢份人本身就同港共政府一鳩樣，行極權主義，有佢講冇人講，從來唔用個腦諗嘢<br />\n所以我已經唔撚想理佢<br />\n<br />\n噚晚佢聲稱有手足搞佢架車，又講到俾手足圍咁<br />\n（事後我發現佢係衝過手足set嘅rb，所以俾一個手足用棍打佢架車）<br />\n佢話咁啱見到有堆警狗嚟緊就有恃無恐，大大力踢咗落手足個春袋度，啲警狗仲放佢走<br />\n佢返到屋企仲好撚得戚咁話睇怕隻曱甴都係冇仔生㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n話我不孝都係咁話，成件事根本係我老豆錯到離晒大譜<br />\n個手足打我老豆架車，我聽我老豆單方面講就不予置評，因為佢平時都成日將曲都拗到直，講嘢極唔可信<br />\n就算真係架車俾人打，都唔撚洗踢人個春袋啊嘛<br />\n最撚仆街係班警狗睇住佢傷人都放佢走<br />\n我阿媽宜家仲話我唔關心佢<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個屋企真係好難生存，幫理不幫親又係錯<br />\n想拉返我個偽中立阿媽做黃<br />\n好撚辛苦，解釋到口都臭佢都淨係幫住老豆<br />\n有冇人教我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f472d2d407f8eee9bc63d9778d23b01f70b6794","tid":1625784,"uid":22833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:22:25.000Z","msg":"一巴車你老豆<br />\n咪撚再返呢個屋企"},{"pid":"fb83c8dc1bb709fcb9a360312c8d316dfe4ae465","tid":1625784,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cbc15e84a240c3270943daae87ddfd6a95323ac","tid":1625784,"uid":244946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"公開你老豆車牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c1732b6b4ac1f1598771f6997c54c980aaebf3","tid":1625784,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cbc15e84a240c3270943daae87ddfd6a95323ac","tid":1625784,"uid":244946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"公開你老豆車牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a010eb613d5cca4b1f0c5312d854c9119deef247","tid":1625784,"uid":226974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:34:57.000Z","msg":"同佢講 你第時係仔送終架啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：家有藍父"},{"pid":"2a8203e0bcf6e712abaeb2406562ce2350f16880","tid":1625784,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"公司 工作崗位之類 車牌車位位置等<br />\n公開得嘅都幫佢公開"},{"pid":"c065959d1b15bb32b398922c6a5a3afcabfd93e8","tid":1625784,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8d14efaab9a7525c3105a16a3c8624a472a386","tid":1625784,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"請報出車輛停泊位置, 車牌<br />\n自然會出現天罰"},{"pid":"e398698e3543820f4eba69998cda26a1eab90254","tid":1625784,"uid":321262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:39:56.000Z","msg":"踢人春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢講出面已經進化到搣睾，叫佢冇事唔好同人嘈"},{"pid":"5b08160b7047587e0a8f3726ef807d328c798637","tid":1625784,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"大義滅親"},{"pid":"386245daa8cbfc13c6f64b3123a9bdd2857b73da","tid":1625784,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"幫手足手麻包袋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f168b1ef2b7a459eb91b067146591229113dd281","tid":1625784,"uid":245626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:04:37.000Z","msg":"老豆好撚驚我阿媽<br />\n噚晚決定每晚同阿媽展開真誠對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感化佢令佢屌鳩我老豆<br />\nBTW老豆架車已爛咗"}]}